summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Eastlake Avenue from Almy Street to Fillmore Street et al in the City of Seattle, by laying Nater Mains etc under Ordinance No. 16604, creating Local Improvement District No. 1532 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
